{"tid":1346023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府強烈譴責在上環及元朗發生的暴力行為","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:01:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7a34d02bb740cf310f398e0e65ffadce5d1c9674","tid":1346023,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】特區政府強烈譴責在上環及元朗發生的暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府指，繼衝擊中聯辦大樓，激進示威者無視警方多次警告，在上環一帶向警方發動連番暴力襲擊，行為令人髮指；與此同時在元朗有人聚眾，在港鐵車站月台及車廂內襲擊乘客，引發衝突，導致有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n港府指香港作為法治社會，完全不能容忍任何暴力行為，予以強烈譴責，會嚴正追究。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/YL-GOV-190722-05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FYL-GOV-190722-05.jpg&h=03882e38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356237&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c22c083e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356237&h=470e8e77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=356237</a>"},{"pid":"dd19d7ca87325e843f27d77809df5001fb678392","tid":1346023,"uid":50658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:22:21.000Z","msg":"上環: 令人髮指<br />\n元朗: 有人受傷<br />\n<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"821949800a4b20c59fd10a89134c5c44f4835667","tid":1346023,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6ae55372b100e96d8f46fd6e0ab43e45f83a37","tid":1346023,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd19d7ca87325e843f27d77809df5001fb678392","tid":1346023,"uid":50658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03: